#. Tag: para
#: using-kmail.docbook:738
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You may find that the standard folders are fine for your needs; "
#| "eventually, though, you will probably need folders to help you organize "
#| "your messages. To create a new folder, select "
